EdgeResistance 250 10
EdgeScroll 100 100
ClickTime 750

DeskTopSize 2x2

ColormapFocus FollowsMouse
# for other parts of the window/borders/icons:
Mouse 1	F	A	Resize-or-Raise
Mouse 1	TS	A	Move-or-Raise
Mouse 1	I	A	Move-or-Iconify
Mouse 3	TSIF	A	RaiseLower

######################## Sample Functions ##########################
AddToFunc Move-or-Raise		I Raise
+				M Move
+  				D Lower

AddToFunc Move-or-Raise2	M Raise
+				M Move
+  				D Lower

AddToFunc Maximize-Func		M Maximize	 0 100
+				C Maximize	 0 80
+				D Maximize	 100 100

AddToFunc Move-or-Iconify	I Raise
+				M Move
+				D Iconify

AddToFunc Resize-or-Raise	I Raise
+				M Resize
+				D Lower

AddToFunc Resize-or-Raise2	M Raise
+				M Resize
+				D Lower

AddToFunc PrintFunction		I Raise
+				I Exec xdpr -id $w

AddToFunc PrintReverseFunction  I Raise
+                               I Exec xdpr 1/2 -h -rv -id $w

AddToFunc Iconify-and-Raise     I Iconify
+                               I Raise

AddToFunc FocusAndWarp I Focus
+                      I WarpToWindow 2p 2p

AddToFunc DeiconifyFocusAndWarp I Iconify -1
+                               I FocusAndWarp

AddToFunc ChangeDefaultFocus I Style * $0
+                            I Recapture

################## FvwmButtons button-bar ################################
*FvwmButtons: Geometry 520x100-1-1
*FvwmButtons: Back bisque3
*FvwmButtons: (Frame 2 Padding 2 2 Container(Rows 2 Columns 5 Frame 1 \
                                             Padding 10 0))
*FvwmButtons: (3x2 Frame 2 Swallow "FvwmIconMan" "Module FvwmIconMan")
*FvwmButtons: (1x2 Frame 2 Swallow(UseOld) "FvwmPager" "Module FvwmPager 0 0")
*FvwmButtons: (1x2 Frame 0 Container(Rows 2 Columns 2 Frame 0))
*FvwmButtons: (End)
*FvwmButtons: (End)
*FvwmIconBox            "Fvwm*"         -

################## Some nice keybinds ###################
Key f A M TrueFullScreen 
Key r A M Restart
Key q A M Close
Key b A M Exec qutebrowser
Key w A M Exec wpa_gui
Key t A M Exec xterm
Key h A M Exec xterm -T htop -e htop
Key u A M Exec uxterm 
Key k A M Next (CurrentDesk, AcceptsFocus) SwitchFocus 
Key j A M Prev (CurrentDesk, AcceptsFocus) SwitchFocus 

DestroyFunc SwitchFocus
AddToFunc SwitchFocus
+ I Iconify off
+ I FlipFocus
+ I Raise
+ I WarpToWindow !raise 5 5

DestroyFunc TrueFullScreen 
AddToFunc TrueFullScreen 
+ I ThisWindow (Maximized) DestroyWindowStyle
+ I TestRc (NoMatch) WindowStyle !Title, !Handles, !Borders, ResizeHintOverride, !Iconifiable, FixedPosition, FixedSize
+ I UpdateStyles
+ I ThisWindow (Maximized) Maximize
+ I TestRc (NoMatch) Maximize ewmhiwa 100 100
